#: src/freqplots/freqplots_core.c:761
msgid ""
"Excitation-port selector: models with more than one EX excitation list every "
"port here.\n"
"\n"
"Entry P<n>: T<tag>/S<seg>\n"
"    n = port number, tag = NEC tag, seg = segment.\n"
"\n"
"Hover an entry to preview that port, click to\n"
"select it, or click away to keep the current one.\n"
"\n"
"Charts that follow the selected port:\n"
"    • Z real / imag\n"
"    • Z magnitude / phase\n"
"    • Smith\n"
"    • VSWR / S11\n"
"    • Net-gain traces (Gain and Viewer gain)\n"
"\n"
"Whole-antenna charts, unaffected by the port:\n"
"    • raw Max gain, Gain direction, F/B\n"
"    • Antenna temperature, G/T"
msgstr ""
"Birač porta pobude: modeli s više od jedne EX pobude ovdje navode svaki "
"port.\n"
"\n"
"Stavka P<n>: T<tag>/S<seg>\n"
"    n = broj porta, tag = NEC oznaka, seg = segment.\n"
"\n"
"Zadržite pokazivač nad stavkom za pregled tog porta, kliknite\n"
"da ga odaberete, ili kliknite izvan da zadržite trenutni.\n"
"\n"
"Grafovi koji prate odabrani port:\n"
"    • Z realno / imag\n"
"    • Z amplituda / faza\n"
"    • Smith\n"
"    • VSWR / S11\n"
"    • Krivulje neto dobitka (Dobitak i Dobitak posmatrača)\n"
"\n"
"Grafovi cijele antene, na koje port ne utiče:\n"
"    • sirovi Maksimalni dobitak, Smjer dobitka, F/B\n"
"    • Temperatura antene, G/T"

